All customers can sign up for direct debit but monthly smart saver customers must pay monthly by direct debit. Customers on standard form contract which register for direct debit will have the amount on each bill deducted by due date.

Credit Card Payment Fee is 0.70%
Australia Post Payment Fee is $2.60
Cheque Payment Fee is $2.60
Dishonour Fee $10.00
Overdue Notice Fee $8.34
For LPG, you are charged by cylinder plus deliver.

For Residential Customers the Daily Supply charge is $0.286 cents per day and Usage charge is $7.98116 per cubic meter.
For Natural Gas you can pay via Standard Form in quarterly bills or you can pay via the Monthly Smart Saver Plan that is paid in monthly instalments. Smaller amounts are frequently paid to remove the vill shock in Winter. Bill is still sent to show how the instalments are tracking in comparison to actual gas cost.

If there is an issue with your direct debit payment, we will attempt to contact you either by email or SMS to let you know of any payments that were not successful.
You will need to pay the amount due by another payment method. You should also login to your My Account to check that your direct debit details are correct.
Banks will charge Kleenheat Gas a fee of $10 if a direct debit is rejected - and that fee will be added to your bill . Late fees will apply if your account isn't paid by another payment method within three days of the payment due by date.

Kleenheat does not offer any concession for our natural gas customers as the energy rebate for gas and electricity usage is funded by the State Government and is controlled by Synergy through your Synergy account.  More detail visit www.synergy.net.au/rebates

Monthly Smart Saver Plan receives 20% off for natural gas charges (24 months). Discount applies to the usage component of the standard tariff which is based on government-regulated capped tariff. The discount does not apply to the supply charge.

We can facilitate a two-week extension for payment, but keep in mind you-ll be ineligible for a Pay On Time discount on the following bill.
